text.__SUMMARY__:
Albizia obbiadensis is a species of legume in the family Fabaceae.
It is found only in Somalia.
text.References: Thulin, M. (1998). "Albizia obbiadensis". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T34515A9872624. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T34515A9872624.en. Retrieved 18 December 2017.
